docs.text:
For full documentation visit mkdocs.org.

#include <iostream>
int main() {
    std::cout << "Hello, World!" << std::endl;
    return 0;
}

def greet():
    print("Hello, World!")
greet()

module hello_world;
  initial begin
    $display("Hello, World!");
    $finish;
  end
endmodule

public class HelloWorld {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello, World!");
    }
}
